少女時代於2009年憑藉〈Gee〉一炮而紅，其單曲被認為是「十年度單曲」（Single of the Decade），亦打破了KBS《音樂銀行》連續多週一位記錄。其單曲被認為是首張獲國際青睞的單曲，有美國[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]的學生為此曲標誌其學習韓國文化的入門曲，亦有許多人表演其知名的舞步<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kr.news.yahoo.com/service/news/shellview.htm?linkid=16&articleid=20090321094731920b6&newssetid=83|date=2009-03-21|accessdate=2012-11-26|publisher=kr.news.yahoo.com|script-title=ko:[단독]소녀시대,하버드大로스쿨 학생들에 '지' 가르친다|language=ko|archive-date=2017-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815140457/http://kr.news.yahoo.com/service/news/shellview.htm?linkid=16&articleid=20090321094731920b6&newssetid=83|dead-url=no}}</ref>。少女時代的知名度亦引申至收入，她們是韓國最炙手可熱的廣告代言人<ref name="bntnews.hankyung.com">{{ko icon}}[http://bntnews.hankyung.com/apps/news?popup=0&nid=04&c1=04&c2=04&c3=00&nkey=200909280929513&mode=sub_view CF 퀸으로 등극한 소녀시대, 광고계도 접수 ('CF Queens SNSD takes over the Advertisement World')] {{Wayback|url=http://bntnews.hankyung.com/apps/news?popup=0&nid=04&c1=04&c2=04&c3=00&nkey=200909280929513&mode=sub_view |date=20160306031807 }}</ref>。少女時代從唱歌、外貌和潮流觸角等多方面的正面評價，市場界人士普遍認為她們是最能影響消費者的名人<ref name="acrofan.com">{{ko icon}}[http://www.acrofan.com/ko-kr/life/news/?mode=view&cate=02&seq=23479&wd=20101222&ucode=00000007&page=1 소녀시대, 가요계-광고계 동시 석권 (Girls Generation Takes Over Music Scene, and Now CF Scene)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.acrofan.com/ko-kr/life/news/?mode=view&cate=02&seq=23479&wd=20101222&ucode=00000007&page=1 |date=20110903063326 }}</ref>。2011年，少女時代在日本製造了5千7百萬美金的銷售總額，其後於韓國創造額外的8千8百56萬美金的銷售總額。2010年9月，日本商業雜誌''Nikkei Business''認為少女時代在國際上的成功媲美[[三星電子|三星電子]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2010/10/02/2010100200238.html|title=Girls' Generation Make Cover of Nikkei Business|date=2010-10-02|accessdate=2012-11-26|publisher=english.chosun.com|archive-date=2013-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105091501/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2010/10/02/2010100200238.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國[[The_Institute_for_Industrial_Policy_Studies|產業政策研究院]]亦認為少女時代是南韓的超級組合<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newswire.co.kr/newsRead.php?no=587227|script-title=ko:산업정책연구원, 대한민국 브랜드 파워 1위수퍼브랜드 선정|year=2011|accessdate=2013-10-31|publisher=newswire.co.kr|language=ko|archive-date=2013-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101225846/http://www.newswire.co.kr/newsRead.php?no=587227|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

少女時代在韓國本土受到廣泛歡迎，獲稱為國內最權威及最具影響力的人物。Sisa Journal分別於2011及2012年選出組合為國內最具影響力的藝人，是史上第一次有女子團體上榜。[[BBC|BBC]]的 ''[[Asia_Today|Asia Today]]'' 於2011年把少女時代選為「韓國強勢領袖50位」中的第45位，是榜上唯一的偶像組合。[[福布斯|富士比]]雜誌於2011年亦表示少女時代是韓國該年最強勢的藝人。

少女時代於5年內奪得韓國多個主要音樂獎項，包括5個演藝大賞。2009年，同一節目憑《Gee》獲得數位媒體大賞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nate.com/view/20101209n29562|date=2010-12-09|accessdate=2012-11-25|publisher=news.nate.com|author=일간스포츠|script-title=ko:[골든] ‘대상’ 소녀시대, "아저씨 팬 실망 안시킬 것"|language=ko|archive-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113004529/http://news.nate.com/view/20101209n29562|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，憑《Oh!》獲得金唱片獎大賞。2011年，憑《The Boys》再次獲得數位媒體大賞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://isplus.live.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=7125308|script-title=ko:소녀시대 "한 곡이 아닌 앨범 전체 사랑해줘 감사"|publisher=Sports Daily|language=ko|date=2012-01-12|accessdate=2012-11-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608072233/http://isplus.live.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=7125308|archivedate=2013-06-08}}</ref>。少女時代是韓國銷量最佳的藝人之一，出道不足5年，已經售出超過3千萬張單曲及4百4十萬張專輯<ref name="McCurry">{{cite news|last=McCurry|first=Justin|title=After Psy's Gangnam Style, here come Korea pop princesses Girls' Generation|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/nov/17/girls-generation-psy-gangnam-k-pop|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2012-11-17|location=London|date=2012-11-17|archive-date=2012-12-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CnjRuEHm?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/nov/17/girls-generation-psy-gangnam-k-pop|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年的專輯《[[The_Boys_(專輯)|The Boys]]》在[[Gaon音乐榜|Gaon Chart]]創下正規專輯最佳銷售記錄<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20140725032032/http://gaonchart.co.kr/chart/album.php?f_chart_kind_cd=T&nationGbn=&f_month=3&f_year=2011&f_type=year South Korea's Gaon Music Chart's Overall Album Sales for 2011 (''The Boys'' #1)] Originally from Gaonchart.co.kr. Archived on July 25, 2014. Retrieved on July 27, 2014.</ref>。其實少女時代發行六張韓語專輯，每次皆售出10萬逾張，是六年以來，韓語音樂市場首次有女子團體能有此成績。團體的成功不限於韓國，其日本出道專輯《Girls' Generation》獲[[RIAJ|日本唱片協會]]認證為「百萬專輯」，以表有一百萬張專輯出貨至日本，是日本Oricon公信榜有史以來銷售量最高的韓國組合<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.riaj.or.jp/data/others/gold/201205.html|title=一般社団法人 日本レコード協会|website=www.riaj.or.jp|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-date=2012-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120611023449/http://www.riaj.or.jp/data/others/gold/201205.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。少女時代亦是韓國傳奇歌手[[李仙姬|李仙姬]]最喜歡的女子團體<ref>[http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=213&aid=0000460713 Lee Sun Hee's favorite girl group is Girls' Generation (in Korean)] News.naver.com (March 25, 2014). Retrieved July 25, 2014.</ref>。首張精選專輯《The BEST》創下了除日本外的亞洲女子組合中獲得Oricon公信榜專輯週榜史上最多冠軍的新紀錄<ref>{{Cite web |url =http://gb.cri.cn/27564/2014/10/29/7791s4745153.htm |title =少女时代《The Best》专辑居日本公信榜 |date =2014-10-29 |publisher =国际在线 |language =zh |accessdate =2015-07-08 |archive-date =2015-07-10 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150710030427/http://gb.cri.cn/27564/2014/10/29/7791s4745153.htm |dead-url =no }}</ref>。

==風格特色==
===音樂路線===
少女時代剛出道時，音樂風格主要為Bubble Gum Pop和[[Teen_Pop|Teen Pop]]。〈Gee〉和〈Oh!〉的單曲皆屬於Bubble Gum Pop和Teen Pop的類別，同時融入舞曲的元素<ref name="interview1">Kim, Hyeon-woo and Jee, Hyeong-joon. [http://news.joins.com/article/3446478.html?ctg=15 소녀시대가 돌아왔다! “9개월만에 컴백, 몸 근질근질했다”(인터뷰①) (''Girls' Generation Has Returned! "Comeback After 9 Months, We're Excited" (Interview Part 1)'')] {{Wayback|url=http://news.joins.com/article/3446478.html?ctg=15 |date=20190522023004 }}. ''[[Joongang_Ilbo|Joins.com]]/Newsen''. January 6, 2009. Retrieved January 5, 2009.</ref><ref name="KenizeOh">{{ko icon}} Yang Ji-won. [http://news.joins.com/article/931/3984931.html?ctg=15 소녀시대, 스키니진→마린룩 이어 이번엔 ‘스포티’ (''Girls' Generation, from Skinny Jeans to Marine Look, Now "Sporty"'')] {{Wayback|url=http://news.joins.com/article/931/3984931.html?ctg=15 |date=20190522135340 }}. ''[[JoongAng_Ilbo|JoongAng Ilbo]]''. January 26, 2010. Retrieved January 26, 2010.</ref>。2009年，隨著發行《說出你願望》，曲風開始轉趨[[電子音樂|電子音樂]]<ref name=sportsseoul>[http://www.sportsseoul.com/news2/entertain/hotentertain/2009/0714/20090714101040100000000_7209885622.html 연예 – 기사내용 – "지금이 소녀시대일까?…아직, 우리시대는 멀었다" (인터뷰)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news2/entertain/hotentertain/2009/0714/20090714101040100000000_7209885622.html |date=20090818021005 }}. Sportsseoul.com (June 13, 2010). Retrieved on October 30, 2011.</ref>。組合於日本以《GIRLS' GENERATION》出道時仍承襲此種曲風，更具電子音樂<ref name=CrazyLondon>{{cite web|title=London is going K-Pop crazy|url=http://www.musicasia.net/london-is-going-k-pop-crazy/|publisher=MusicAsia|accessdate=2011-11-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120221916/http://www.musicasia.net/london-is-going-k-pop-crazy/|archivedate=2011-11-20}}</ref>的風格<ref>{{cite web|url=http://seoulbeats.com/2012/06/side-b-shoujo-jidai-brings-the-fans-out/|title=Side B: Shoujo Jidai Brings the Fans Out|date=2012-06-16|accessdate=2012-10-02|publisher=seoulbeats.com|author=Subi|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BhcQdZgj?url=http://seoulbeats.com/2012/06/side-b-shoujo-jidai-brings-the-fans-out/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其後的兩張日語專輯及单曲《PAPARAZZI》和 《FLOWER POWER》亦繼續採用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sponichi.co.jp/entertainment/news/2012/10/02/kiji/K20121002004238120.html|title=少女時代　シングル１位！１０年９月の日本デビュー以来初|date=2012-10-02|accessdate=2012-11-26|publisher=sponichi.co.jp|archive-date=2012-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004043157/http://www.sponichi.co.jp/entertainment/news/2012/10/02/kiji/K20121002004238120.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。韓語專輯大量與製作人劉英振和[[Kenzie|Kenzie]]合作<ref name="KenizeOh" /><ref>{{cite news|last=Kang|first=Myoung-seok|title=Record producer Yoo Young-jin – Part 2|url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2010061113544954123|accessdate=2012-05-20|newspaper=10 Asia|date=2010-06-11|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203005834/http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2010061113544954123|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌詞方面，勇於表達女性平權，歌曲〈Hoot〉和〈The Boys〉可見一斑<ref name="ryan">{{cite web |url=http://ryanseacrest.com/2011/10/18/k-pop-group-girls-generation-release-english-version-of-the-boys-video/ |title=K-Pop Group ‘Girls’ Generation’ Release English Version of ‘The Boys’ |accessdate=2011-10-23 |publisher=Ryan Seacrest |author=Jen Erenza |date=October 2011 |archive-date=2011-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111020105910/http://ryanseacrest.com/2011/10/18/k-pop-group-girls-generation-release-english-version-of-the-boys-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首位參與創作組合作品的成員是俞利，於三輯《Hoot》時一起編寫R&B曲風的〈Mistake〉(내 잘못이죠) <ref>{{cite web|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1010250031|title=소녀시대 유리 첫 작사곡 선보인다..정통 R&B 공략|date=2010-10-25|accessdate=2012-12-11|publisher=osen.t.co.kr|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203010441/http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1010250031|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其後蒂芬妮和秀英於第三張韓語專輯《The Boys》時分別合作編寫〈The Boys〉和〈How Great is Your Love〉<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=003&aid=0004142436 |script-title=ko:소녀시대, 경구 되살리다…소년들이여 야망 가져라 :: 네이버 뉴스 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-02-12 |language=ko |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203014755/http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=003&aid=0004142436 }}</ref>。四輯《I Got a Boy》揉合多種音樂元素，包括[[New_wave_music|80s new wave]]、[[電子舞曲|電子舞曲]] 和 [[Contemporary_R&B|現代R&B]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|title=Girls' Generation, 'I Got A Boy': Track-By-Track Review|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/1481602/girls-generation-i-got-a-boy-track-by-track-review|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=2013-01-04|archive-date=2013-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529183330/http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/1481602/girls-generation-i-got-a-boy-track-by-track-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而其單曲〈I Got a Boy〉是融入流行、復古和城市類型的電子舞曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://girlsgeneration.smtown.com/ |title=Girls Generation Official Website |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2013-02-12 |archive-date=2010-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100109001519/http://girlsgeneration.smtown.com/ }}</ref>，〈Romantic St.〉被Naver Music歸類為[[jazz|jazz]]和Swing music類別<ref name="naver">{{cite web|url=http://music.naver.com/album/index.nhn?albumId=359839|title=I Got A Boy - 4th album by Girls' Generation|date=2013-01-01|accessdate=2013-11-04|language=ko|publisher=[[Naver|Naver Music]]|archive-date=2016-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109142431/http://music.naver.com/album/index.nhn?albumId=359839|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國告示牌雜誌形容〈FLOWER POWER〉為重和諧、Robo-pop Jam；〈I Got a Boy〉不停從 drum 'n' bass 和重電子流行樂跳換；〈GALAXY SUPERNOVA〉具有強勁的節拍背樂；而〈Do the Catwalk〉則擁有瑯瑯上口的吸引力<ref>{{cite news|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|title=Girls' Generation Releases 'Galaxy Supernova' in Japan|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/5695513/girls-generation-releases-galaxy-supernova-in-japan|accessdate=2013-11-29|newspaper=Billboard|date=2013-09-17|archive-date=2014-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711042742/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/5695513/girls-generation-releases-galaxy-supernova-in-japan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。〈Mr.Mr.〉是一首[[节奏布鲁斯|R&B]]风格的舞曲，由音乐制作团队The Underdogs打造，是少女时代与The Underdogs的首次合作。

===公眾形象===
在早期職業生涯中，少女時代以淡妝及清純羞澀的少女形象出道<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mediaus.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=14626 |title=소녀시대는 어떻게 시대의 총아가 되었나 – 미디어스 |3= |accessdate=2013-02-12 |language=ko |archive-date=2013-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525123148/http://www.mediaus.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=14626 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。2009年推出的首張迷你專輯《Gee》是少女時代的成名作品，透過單色襯衫和牛仔褲的配搭凸顯出組合的活力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=111&aid=0000137503|title=별 "소녀시대, 음악 넘어선 아이콘!"|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-date=2013-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105141135/http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=111&aid=0000137503|dead-url=no}}</ref>。向來以清純形象示人的少女時代，在第二張迷你專輯《說出你願望》中選挑選了成熟性感的形象，透過海軍陸戰隊服裝配搭熱褲加上獨特的Jegi-kicking dance({{lang|ko|제기차기 춤}})和Leg-beauty dance({{lang|ko|각선미 춤}})凸顯出成員的美腿特徵，更獲得「美腿組合」的評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/uhtml/read.jsp?idxno=2009062620283612085|title='컴백' 소녀시대, '군무' 퍼포먼스 일단 '합격점'|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182703/http://www.asiae.co.kr/uhtml/read.jsp?idxno=2009062620283612085|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。第二張正規專輯《Oh!》的啦啦隊概念使晉身為一線女團。<ref>{{cite news |language = ko |author = Choi Jong-pyeon |url = http://news.sbs.co.kr/section_news/news_read.jsp?news_id=N1000702214 |title = 장동건-고소영 '5월 결혼설'…아이티 동반 방문 추진 (''Jang Dong-geun–Go So-young "Wedding in May"...IT Company Interview Propulsion'') |publisher = SBS |date = 2010-01-26 |accessdate = 2014-12-20 |archive-date = 2014-11-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141117183748/http://news.sbs.co.kr/section_news/news_read.jsp?news_id=N1000702214 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。《Oh!》的專輯改版《Run Devil Run》，少女時代首次挑戰黑暗性感的形象並以「黑暗少時」為主題<ref>[http://star.mt.co.kr/view/stview.php?no=2010031711450033387&outlink=2&SVEC '블랙소시' 윤아•티파니가 마지막에 공개된 이유] {{Wayback|url=http://star.mt.co.kr/view/stview.php?no=2010031711450033387&outlink=2&SVEC |date=20141129082428 }}《머니투데이》, 2010년 3월 17일</ref>。繼《Oh!》與《Run Devil Run》獲得成功後，第三張迷你專輯《Hoot》以[[邦德女郎|邦德女郎]]形象再次回歸<ref>{{cite web|url=http://article.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=6819071|title=소녀티 벗을래 … 복고풍 잊어줘|publisher=article.joinsmsn.com|date=2011-12-05|accessdate=2012-11-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310130910/http://news.joins.com/article/6819071|archivedate=2016-03-10}}</ref>。2011年，第三張正規專輯《The Boys》使用了「女強人」形象，成員選擇自己合適的服裝以強調自己品味<ref>{{cite web|title=Rino Nakasone Official Twitter Page|url=http://twitter.com/#!/RinOkinawa/status/62774234774110208|publisher=Microblog at Twitter.com|accessdate=2011-07-03|archive-date=2018-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126141023/https://twitter.com/#!/RinOkinawa/status/62774234774110208|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。2013年，第四張正規專輯《I Got a Boy》採用嘻哈女孩形象回歸，成功塑造全新的少女時代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=109&aid=0002461705|title=소녀시대, 하이힐 벗는다... 퍼포먼스 난이도↑|date=2012-11-27|publisher=news.naver.com|language=Ko|accessdate=2014-12-03|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203014315/http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=109&aid=0002461705|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在美國雜誌《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》中，John Seabrook對少女時代的評論提到：「a group of preppy-looking young women in skinny trousers. When they wear hot pants, it's to display the gams, not the glutes.」（一隊看來像私校預科生的年輕女性們穿著緊身牛仔褲。當她們穿熱褲，是為了秀腿（優雅），不是露臀（不雅）。）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2012/10/08/factory-girls-2|title=Factory Girls|first=John|last=Seabrook|date=2012-10-01|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-20|via=www.newyorker.com|archive-date=2019-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724200424/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2012/10/08/factory-girls-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{link-en|紐約雜誌|New York (magazine)}}》表示少女時代在[[韓國流行音樂|韓國流行音樂]]受歡迎程度的決定性因素並不是因為音樂本身，而是公眾喜歡她們的長相和個性以及散發出的謙遜和友好一面給每一個粉絲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nymag.com/thecut/2012/10/grown-men-moved-by-south-korean-girl-groups.html|title=Grown Men Creepily Moved by South Korean Girl Groups|publisher=New York Magazine|date=2012-10-01|accessdate=2014-12-03|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BhcS863T?url=http://nymag.com/thecut/2012/10/grown-men-moved-by-south-korean-girl-groups.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。英國音樂週刊《[[新音樂快遞|新音樂快遞]]》中Kevin Perry寫道：「Girls' Generation also have a massive nine members, which is indicative of the way the efficient K-pop machine can favour choreographed style over individual personalities.」（少女時代有足足九個人，足以證明在效率很高的韓式音樂比較偏於團體編舞，多於團員的個人特色）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/blog/index.php?blog=1&title=korea_prospects_a_beginner_s_guide_to_k_&more=1&c=1&tb=1&pb=1|title=Game of Thrones: How the Seven are going to protect the suicide squad|date=2017-08-15|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525045307/http://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/beyond-gangnam-style-a-beginner%E2%80%99s-guide-to-k-pop|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==慈善公益==
2010年2月4日聯同音樂網站 Lunchbox 的 "Music Dream" 計畫舉辦捐款活動。銷售總額的3%捐於韓國[[願望成真基金|願望成真基金]]。

2011年4月27日發行的日語單曲《[[Mr._Taxi/Run_Devil_Run|MR.TAXI]]》和《Run Devil Run》，其部份收入捐於日本[[紅十字會|紅十字會]]，用於協助[[東日本大震災|2011年東日本大地震及海嘯]]的災民<ref>{{Cite news|script-title=ko:[애프터스토리]일본 대지진으로 활동 연기된 소녀시대, 뭐하나 봤더니|url=http://news.nate.com/view/20110414n13640|accessdate=2011-06-16|newspaper=Nate|author=이정혁|agency=Nate|language=ko|archive-date=2014-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112124039/http://news.nate.com/view/20110414n13640|dead-url=no}}</ref>。組合亦曾經拍賣簽名手提包用以籌款<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/0311disaster/recovery/AJ201203210015|date=2011-03-21|accessdate=2012-11-25|publisher=ajw.ashai.com|author=KAZUYA OMURO|title=K-pop stars donate memorabilia to help quake victims|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102044730/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/0311disaster/recovery/AJ201203210015|archivedate=2012-11-02}}</ref>。8月9日與同公司的[[f(x)_(組合)|f(x)]]和[[SHINee|SHINee]]攜手協助非洲兒童。[[聯合國|聯合國]]秘書長[[潘基文|潘基文]]與組合一起參與由韓國紅十字會和[[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]韓國委員會安排的《幫助非洲兒童計畫》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soompi.com/2011/08/10/snsd-and-other-celebrities-join-un-secretarygeneral-ban-ki-moons-help-african-children/|title=SNSD and Other Celebrities Join UN Secretary-General Ban Ki Moon's "Help African Children"|publisher=soompi.com|author=hazelnutthursdays|date=2011-08-10|accessdate=2012-08-27|archive-date=2012-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031104025/http://www.soompi.com/2011/08/10/snsd-and-other-celebrities-join-un-secretarygeneral-ban-ki-moons-help-african-children/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月11日在時任韓國總統夫人金潤玉女士帶領下，少女時代獲選為《2010－2012年韓國訪問年》觀光大使。計畫為韓國政府致力於2012年底前最少吸引1千萬外國旅客到訪韓國，希望藉著組合一時無兩的知名度打響頭炮<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.visitkoreayear.com/english/community/community_01_01_01_view.asp?bidx=205&st&sech&page=1|title=Girls` Generation Appointed as Honorary Ambassadors for the Visit Korea Year Campaign|date=2011-08-08|accessdate=2012-07-12|publisher=english.visitkoreayear.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130324233051/http://english.visitkoreayear.com/english/community/community_01_01_01_view.asp?bidx=205&st&sech&page=1|archivedate=2013-03-24}}</ref>。9月17日聯同Super Junior在KBS的''Love Request''節目特輯中亮相，邀請一位11歲有心臟問題的柬埔寨女孩和失明男孩前往韓國接受治療，亦探訪一位終身皆與其寡母居於酒店的韓國女孩。這兩隊組合亦參與其後的捐血活動。在85分鐘的放送中，籌得超過3千2百萬韓圜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soshified.com/2011/09/girls-generation-appears-on-love-request|title=Girls’ Generation Appears on ‘Love Request’|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-date=2017-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170704165552/http://www.soshified.com/2011/09/girls-generation-appears-on-love-request|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月27日，和韓國的WoongJin Coway公司於首爾市時代廣場舉辦「美麗拍賣」活動，協助遭受家庭暴力的女士。藉由拍賣廣告穿過的服飾做慈善籌款<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wonderfulgeneration.net/2011/10/snsd-at-special-charity-auction-event.html|title=Loading...|website=www.wonderfulgeneration.net|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-date=2016-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514032609/http://www.wonderfulgeneration.net/2011/10/snsd-at-special-charity-auction-event.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年3月7日，首爾市江南區宣佈委任少女時代為首爾市[[江南區_(首爾)|江南區]]宣傳大使。同年4月韓國失明防治協會宣佈組合將會成為《韓國失明防治》宣傳大使<ref>{{cite web|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joinsmsn.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=2951234|title=Girls' Generation to be eye candy for anti-blindness movement|date=2012-04-09|accessdate=2012-07-08|publisher=koreajoongangdaily.joinsmsn.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608093926/http://koreajoongangdaily.joinsmsn.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=2951234|archivedate=2013-06-08}}</ref>。8月17日，媒體報導少女時代把服飾捐給慈善團體用於籌款<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nate.com/view/20120816n14244&mid=e0403&cid=374678|title=[걸,옷] "컴플렉스, 어떻게 가릴까?"…무대의상 궁금증 '9'|publisher=news.nate.com|date=2012-08-16|accessdate=2012-08-17|language=ko|archive-date=2014-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112085427/http://news.nate.com/view/20120816n14244%26mid%3De0403%26cid%3D374678|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同一星期，韓國郵政宣佈銷售組合官方郵票所得利潤將捐於慈善團體Merry Year。12月5日捐贈8公噸大米，估計援助66,400人<ref>{{cite news|title=(Korean)"소녀시대, 강남구에 사랑의 쌀 전달|url=http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=102&oid=003&aid=0004864051|accessdate=2013-01-11|newspaper=Naver|date=2012-12-05|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629073515/http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=102&oid=003&aid=0004864051|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=(Korean)소녀시대가 기부한 쌀 8t 알고 보니…팬들이 십시일반 모아|url=http://article.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=10082026|accessdate=2013-01-11|newspaper=joinmsn|date=2012-12-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130206003943/http://article.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=10082026|archivedate=2013-02-06}}</ref>。

